OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FTuesday will get off to a dry
OL,6,Fstart with some bright spells.
OL,7,FHowever, cloud will gradually increase
OL,8,Ffrom the west, with some showers
OL,9,Fbreaking out during the afternoon.
OL,10,FThese could turn heavy later. Feeling
OL,11,Fwarm in the brighter breaks.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FEarly showers will die out
OL,14,Fduring the evening to leave a largely
OL,15,Fdry night. Some clear intervals,
OL,16,Falthough low cloud, and some mist and
OL,17,Ffog patches are likely to form.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
