OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FEarly low cloud and mist
OL,6,Fwill soon lift to leave a fine day
OL,7,Facross the region. It will be dry,
OL,8,Falthough with fairly cloudy skies
OL,9,Fpersisting sunshine will be hazy.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,12,FOvernight rain should soon clear on
OL,13,FThursday to leave plenty of sunshine
OL,14,Ffor the afternoon. Largely dry and
OL,15,Fsettled thereafter too, and starting
OL,16,Fto feel warmer again in the sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
